{"tid":2037204,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"賭場莊家(或毒販等等)有冇罪過?","createTime":"2020-05-27T00:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T00:58:32.000Z","uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3470b7266dc6a04b851d72938ce4b026e4c04561","tid":2037204,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:53:43.000Z","msg":"有一位師兄話:<br />\n<br />\n家破人亡，係d 人自己羅黎，冇人迫佢地賭場賭錢的，關何生咩事？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我的見解:<br />\n<br />\n先不論賭徒<br />\n<br />\n我論賭檔，賭檔經營者明白，佢開賭檔呢個動作，會令好多人上癮，會整死好多人，死人仲要唔係果個人死左咁簡單，而係牽連甚廣!  同埋對 &ldquo;整體的顧客&quot; 並無得益(咁當然有極少數顧客贏左大錢即刻收手並絕跡賭場)<br />\n<br />\n賭業可振興當地經濟，GDP，收入等等，澳門是表表者，但賭業可否&ldquo;振興&rdquo;整個國家的經濟，或者人世間的&quot;快樂美善?   賭博產生的血海深仇，似一個漣漪在人間發散開去，這種思想心理情緒是微妙地傳播出去，不可能那麼容易被觀察到，相信會對整個國家，甚至全世界有大大負面效果，這效果極間接而且微妙<br />\n<br />\n當然，你話係d賭徒自己攞黎，亦無可厚非"},{"pid":"578faeca275861d2cde0a5bfea8a8aec48c7f28e","tid":2037204,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:55:11.000Z","msg":"咩係罪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/peT8V93.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpeT8V93.png&h=419e79fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4d35737c6468ac3de8c125d11d4b22ef1dd0c2db","tid":2037204,"uid":333380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:56:33.000Z","msg":"咁開麥當勞都罪過啦<br />\n明知垃圾食物影響健康都賣比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78be78f9ac7c5f74dd730fec2358b094e2f642d1","tid":2037204,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:58:32.000Z","msg":"依照佢地邏輯<br />\n毒販 馬伕都冇罪<br />\n毒販 班垃圾自己食冰死 係d吸毒仔自己攞黎<br />\n馬伕 班垃圾自己叫雞唔戴套中性病 係d文員仔自己攞黎"}]}